Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.83,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}与你牵手 和你相随
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:27.92,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的温暖 让我变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.95,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}那是我一个人 即便大大地展开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:38.76,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}也不足以拥抱的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.81,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}现在 我们一起来拥抱它吧
