Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.61,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}飞越过勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:55.19,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}等待我们的是美丽的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:58.24,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}向着梦想飞翔的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.33,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}正迎接百花盛开的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:05.66,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}梦想一定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.12,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\blur1\fad(200,200)}相信着 我们能够飞翔
