Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:15.53,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}記憶の中で溢れる Love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.78,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}駆け足な Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.83,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}手を繋いで Time goes by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:27.92,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}強くなれたんだ その温もりで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.95,INKanata,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}一人きりじゃ もう両手いっぱい広げても
